  "detailed_description": "<i>\"Welcome to the <strong>OLD Future</strong>, a post-apocalyptic indie survival game set in a Sand-Box world inspired by classic dystopian games we all grew up with.<br><br><i><strong>Early Access Content Status:</strong></i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1678250/extras/8b3d6adea1e3f0d306ac7059f381f878.avif?t=1737597645\" width=600 height=192 /></span><br>\"Step into a world where a powerful civilization, fueled by the power of the ATOM, suddenly vanishes in a single afternoon. Explore the ruins, uncover the secrets, and unravel the mystery of their downfall in this post-apocalyptic adventure.<br><br>Embark on an epic adventure as you awaken in a desolate future. Search the ruins of a once-thriving world and discover hidden treasures among the debris. Navigate treacherous landscapes and unravel the mysteries of this long-forgotten era. Are you ready to claim your place among the legends of tomorrow?\"<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1678250/extras/75d2c976ec95a5dcbfe80ade746cf8fd.avif?t=1737597645\" width=600 height=186 /></span><br><br>Friends, this is a Solo Dev project, all feedback is much appreciated!<br><br><i><strong>Game Features: </strong></i><br>✔Inventory & gear<br>✔Crafting & Survival<br>✔Weapons, upgrades & various ammo.<br>✔Traders, beasts & AI<br>✔House building, upgrades & locks<br>✔Nature biomes: Nuclear winter, Wasteland, Paradise, Old West.<br>✔Current Maps: Canyon, Paradise Island.<br>✔Multicamera & Minimap<br>✔Local & Internet Multiplayer <br>✔Multiplayer Chat & Guild manager<br>✔Download size ~6 Gb<br>🎵Soundtrack: 83 Tracks v0.1.2.9🎵<br><br>Please join me in making this game a reality.</i>",
  "about_the_game": "<i>\"Welcome to the <strong>OLD Future</strong>, a post-apocalyptic indie survival game set in a Sand-Box world inspired by classic dystopian games we all grew up with.<br><br><i><strong>Early Access Content Status:</strong></i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1678250/extras/8b3d6adea1e3f0d306ac7059f381f878.avif?t=1737597645\" width=600 height=192 /></span><br>\"Step into a world where a powerful civilization, fueled by the power of the ATOM, suddenly vanishes in a single afternoon. Explore the ruins, uncover the secrets, and unravel the mystery of their downfall in this post-apocalyptic adventure.<br><br>Embark on an epic adventure as you awaken in a desolate future. Search the ruins of a once-thriving world and discover hidden treasures among the debris. Navigate treacherous landscapes and unravel the mysteries of this long-forgotten era. Are you ready to claim your place among the legends of tomorrow?\"<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1678250/extras/75d2c976ec95a5dcbfe80ade746cf8fd.avif?t=1737597645\" width=600 height=186 /></span><br><br>Friends, this is a Solo Dev project, all feedback is much appreciated!<br><br><i><strong>Game Features: </strong></i><br>✔Inventory & gear<br>✔Crafting & Survival<br>✔Weapons, upgrades & various ammo.<br>✔Traders, beasts & AI<br>✔House building, upgrades & locks<br>✔Nature biomes: Nuclear winter, Wasteland, Paradise, Old West.<br>✔Current Maps: Canyon, Paradise Island.<br>✔Multicamera & Minimap<br>✔Local & Internet Multiplayer <br>✔Multiplayer Chat & Guild manager<br>✔Download size ~6 Gb<br>🎵Soundtrack: 83 Tracks v0.1.2.9🎵<br><br>Please join me in making this game a reality.</i>",
